Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出入这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.41,0:00:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 房间里竟然有这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画 漫画 游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.17,0:00:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么低级的趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hellhound
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不择手段 立刻给我把春香找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃木坂家的长女 居然染上了这种低俗的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅 绝不原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【我很喜欢...】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人 我...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的爱好被父亲知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一回到家 父亲正等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在屋子里的周边都被翻出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被翻遍了么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夏季同人会上买的东西也被没收了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还被狠狠摔在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易费尽辛苦买来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲还做了很多过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本不听我的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要把我带回去么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲不改变主意我是不会回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是叶月小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 如果这是您的意思 我会追随您的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不会扔下你一个人的 我要伴您左右
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的侍女呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似有情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里 由香里老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都知道了 住我家里也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“什么”的意思是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无家可归别无归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的爸妈都出国了 家里正好有空房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才住在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了裕人 脸好红哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说 我可没乱想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不信不信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不要给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有 一点都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人真是大胆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不许搞不纯异性交友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要搞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人脸好红
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是 想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了 你们吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 小春香和小女仆入住凌濑家的欢迎派对现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑠子姐姐好强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酒量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如果当秘书的话 酒量不强不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以平时才经常锻炼 好努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可没有那么高尚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}【我是BH女】
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}【那样】
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想有一天能变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}【那样】
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人 这个火锅是你...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是现成的 就随便拿来用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮出来的东西很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合当夫婿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小裕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别粘着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多话要问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:06:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于小春香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很关心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人 快点从实招来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很关心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么时候开始好上的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 我和春香也不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都直呼她的名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和春香...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是普通的同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的不是说...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然关系特殊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人就爽快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身为春香小姐的女仆 有知道的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是好奇心使然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四目凝视
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系真是不一般啊 这个色男
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我快点说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点做过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他害羞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你们同居了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 这么下去就是姐夫 还是孩子他爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你那边的情况怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然父亲派出密探去了夏季同人会的会场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲的直属部队Hellhound
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直译的话就是地狱门犬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这里安全吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持23个小时吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计明天就有援兵到达
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级强大的无敌最终兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可靠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是初夜 你对姐姐要温柔点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:07:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 早 熟 了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都睡着了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我醒着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}【惊】
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 可以请你照顾春香小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样睡会着凉的 请您把她带回卧室里去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个倒没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要在附近巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡逻？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 保护春香小姐的人身安全是我身为女仆的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里跟在家不同 充满了不安因素
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:09:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看起来怎么不像…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这次我真的出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是假动作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离裕人的脸这么近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是公主抱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对面 春香正在...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在胡想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 裕人 你没睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我可以进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 房间好黑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是晚上嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确...确实 可不只是因为那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 好黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人呆在黑漆漆的地方你不会寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 你不敢一个人睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家里可以抱着公仔睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月小姐她们也会巡逻 所以不会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 那个...我能在这里睡一晚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来不想打扰你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请...请…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请陪陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《innocent Smile》的创刊号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这个就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我离开家的时候 只抢了这个出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本书对于我来说很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是非常非常重要的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能睡得着嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如…如果可以 能牵着我的手么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...不愿意就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要牵手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香 很不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 不管发生什么 我会都和你在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春...香？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到目标 重复 捕捉到目标
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等哦 早餐马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏 怎么了 这么急
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了 姐姐的行踪被爸爸发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面有追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被…被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人开门 我就自己进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把春香交还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄冬老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然砍上来 真是无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闯到别人家里来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无礼的到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按过门铃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑠子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人你快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按住她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开 给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你碍事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香 我可找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 跟我回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的事我已经不介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你一时鬼迷心窍对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你也不可能喜欢上那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再幼稚了 回到原本的你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不觉得自己做错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲你根本不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是喜欢那些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢《迷糊姑娘小秋》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢《熬夜恶魔比洛》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢《夜想曲女学园》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最最喜欢《innocent Smile》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决不是一时的鬼迷心窍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法认同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:17:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不该沉迷于动漫这些东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个小鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个小鬼骗了春香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么不可原谅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香的爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那么见不得人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种低俗的东西 与她乃木坂家长女的身份不符
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么资格这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道春香的爱好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有想过春香为什么喜欢这些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是怀着什么样的心情喜欢这些的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香对于自己的爱好 和其他的人都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心一意 那么努力而又认真
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是发自内心地去享受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有秋叶原系不被大家认同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么怪异吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这帮混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子是赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不明摆着嘛 我是来阻止父亲的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡闹什么 小孩子快退下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为该退下的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么看我觉得都是你不对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香各方面都那么用功
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这么一个小小的爱好 你就不要反对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴 不用你多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说我多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香是我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我关心她是应该的 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不...这个...确实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真的理解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.45,0:20:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香 还有裕人所说的话 你都赞同吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可...可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是相信他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不太了解动漫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是春香自己的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自己第一次开始做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不相信她 又让谁去相信她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些话你不说我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 这还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了 爸爸好像认同你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们胜诉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜二位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子 我可不会容忍到这个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点放开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先回邸宅了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰到你们真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香 为了以后自己的爱好得到认同 可要好好学习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你们添了不少麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.64,0:21:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说我多少有点头脑充血  但所作所为确实有失成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里 我说话也有点过分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接触过不少人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:22:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是敢那么直接跟我直抒己见的人  你还是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.53,0:22:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌濑裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记住你的名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 这样事情就解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起吃早餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还果然还睡得死猪一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起吃早饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.00,0:24:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏小姐约了裕人少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.39,0:24:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是要约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.94,0:24:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.24,0:24:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 好不容易约次会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.22,0:24:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稚菜姐姐突然出现并且非常大胆地亲热 闹出好大事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.29,0:24:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.07,0:24:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃木坂春香的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.67,0:24:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大~哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.05,0:24:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直扑你的怀抱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:21.68,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半分ならあげない　すべて奪って欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:28.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運命なら一秒　生まれ変わる夢を見た
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:34.67,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,クチビルを噛んで　痛いほど高ぶっちゃうね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:37.81,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でもしょうがない　戻れない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:42.05,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ...　これが愛なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:43.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do!しよう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:45.23,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふるえる　ふるえる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:49.35,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やわらかな核心に触れてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:55.18,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひどい苦さの後で　ほとばしる甘い夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:58.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ホラ　つながる　つながる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:02.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絡みつく視線で　つかまえて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:07.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「わたしのこと大好きですか？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:10.84,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おねがい　Bitter Tune
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:15.82,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離さないで...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:21.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一半？不给你 要就全部夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:28.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运？下一秒 梦见我的重生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:34.67,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧咬嘴唇 痛感伴随高昂的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:37.81,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是人家没办法 已经无法回头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:42.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我...这就叫做爱吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:43.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:45.23,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颤抖 颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:49.35,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我碰到了那软绵绵的核心部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:55.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无比苦涩之后 是止不的美梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:58.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 我们在一起 在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:02.31,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用娇滴滴的视线将你抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:07.48,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"你很喜欢我吗？"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:10.84,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 Bitter Tune
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:15.82,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要离开我...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.46,0:22:56.20,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だいじなトコで　ねえジャマをしないで！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:11.69,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まさに　手と手が触れた瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:13.46,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あら　ちっ·ちっ·ちっ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:17.14,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,オジャマ虫やってくる　イエイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.44,0:23:21.47,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かなり絶妙です　タイミング
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.69,0:23:25.93,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぐずぐず　してはいられない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:30.44,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うわさのあの娘も　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.87,0:23:34.69,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ピンキィーに　頬っぺた染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:40.27,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言いたくて　でも言えない　それは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:45.80,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,てっぺんに「ス」の付く言葉です
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.93,0:23:51.85,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,コイをしたいなら　よっといで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.54,0:23:56.84,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花しょって　夢しょって　歌いましょう　らんらんらん
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.99,0:24:00.96,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ワケワカンナイ！？　そりゃLOVEなんですもん
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.49,0:24:03.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,くちびるが動いて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:06.31,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でも　ここからは“ヒミチュ”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:08.34,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人さしゆび　ゆびっ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.88,0:24:10.94,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ナイショ·モード　ひそひそっ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.46,0:22:56.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键时刻 不要捣乱！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:11.69,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正当他们要手碰手时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:13.46,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 嘻 嘻 嘻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:17.14,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们去当电灯泡 Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.44,0:23:21.47,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常绝妙的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.69,0:23:25.93,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可不能磨磨蹭蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:30.44,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的那个女孩 也一定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.87,0:23:34.69,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是绯红的脸蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:40.27,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说 却说不出口 那个词
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:45.80,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是“喜”字开头的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.93,0:23:51.85,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要恋爱？那就快行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.54,0:23:56.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像花 像梦 让我们歌唱 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.99,0:24:00.96,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一头雾水！？ 这就叫做爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.49,0:24:03.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴唇轻启
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:06.31,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 接下去就是“秘密”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:08.34,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食指放在嘴唇上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.88,0:24:10.94,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贴着你的耳边 悄悄地...
